quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,"Alif Lām Ra. Those are the signs1of the Evident Scripture."
  12,2,"Indeed, We have sent it down as an Arabic Recital1, that youpl may reason."
  12,3,"We relate to yousg the most beautiful of stories by revealing to you this Recitalf , although prior to it you were indeed one of the oblivious."
  12,4,"Recall when Joseph said to his father, “O my father, I saw eleven planets and the sun and the moon; I saw them prostrating to me.”"